  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/a3180900ed528d3081ffcefd7d344b02.avif?t=1757938761\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create Your Own Task Force From Scratch</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>You are both the leader and the operator in the battlefield. Train your squad, purchase better equipment, and lead your men to fight various crime factions all around your country </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shoot, Command, Lead! You Are On The Battlefield!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/953430bbf74752a042b4ff1251e38a51.poster.avif?t=1757938761\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/953430bbf74752a042b4ff1251e38a51.webm?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/953430bbf74752a042b4ff1251e38a51.mp4?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a playable character as well as a team leader. You can participate in every engagement, or you can command the entire action from a distance</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plan Your Entry</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/e844dea1ff25e82b1de53167208f5ecc.poster.avif?t=1757938761\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/e844dea1ff25e82b1de53167208f5ecc.webm?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/e844dea1ff25e82b1de53167208f5ecc.mp4?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple yet powerful command system where you can plan every engagement with grenades, special gadgets, and, of course, your own strategic thinking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Execute Your Plan</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/ac113bf4041caad3511769d07d5b929e.poster.avif?t=1757938761\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/ac113bf4041caad3511769d07d5b929e.webm?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/ac113bf4041caad3511769d07d5b929e.mp4?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every shootout is dangerous, and mistakes will be painful</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Buy, Maintain, and Equip Gear</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/9ea521886f2a8e386ded16264c5fd2ab.poster.avif?t=1757938761\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/9ea521886f2a8e386ded16264c5fd2ab.webm?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/9ea521886f2a8e386ded16264c5fd2ab.mp4?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your loadout with everything you need, from weapons and armor to specialized gadgets and grenades. Everything you need is available to purchase in the store. It’s your job to make true professionals out of ordinary recruits. Train them, pay them, buy gear for them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dive Into An Immersive Campaign</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/4ebe94d823fe1d8ceb4e1c639f5cc176.poster.avif?t=1757938761\" width=646 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/4ebe94d823fe1d8ceb4e1c639f5cc176.webm?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/4ebe94d823fe1d8ceb4e1c639f5cc176.mp4?t=1757938761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision you make matters. Will you rise as a respected leader who can save your country from downfall?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598610/extras/2a6700f4e25e0a45db1688f6aec1c962.avif?t=1757938761\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p>",
